PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the N'QUATQUA INDIAN BAND surrenders, for a term of 49 years, some 0.130 hectares of land on Nequatque Indian Reserve No. 1, in British Columbia, in order to allow them to be leased for the operation of a gasoline retail outlet or a convenience store, or both.
